59
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:40,488
I'll see her first.

60
00:04:46,369 --> 00:04:47,412
Bring me the laptop.

61
00:04:59,257 --> 00:05:00,967
You think I can't find you, right?

62
00:05:01,968 --> 00:05:03,219
FROM YANG JONG-HOON

63
00:05:06,055 --> 00:05:06,931
PROFESSOR KANG JU-MAN

64
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,980
What brings you here at this hour?

65
00:05:14,689 --> 00:05:15,940
Please take a seat.

66
00:05:20,862 --> 00:05:22,322
