01:01:25,306 --> 01:01:27,350
then used it to get into the Law School.

944
01:01:27,433 --> 01:01:31,229
Just as Prof. Yang said, I do not think
we should condone any illegal acts

945
01:01:31,312 --> 01:01:33,940
in the admission process
of the Law School.

946
01:01:38,820 --> 01:01:40,363
Just as Prof. Yang said,

947
01:01:41,239 --> 01:01:44,617
you bribed the school,
called it a donation, then got to teach.

948
01:01:44,701 --> 01:01:47,495
I don't think
that's something for you to say.

949
01:01:49,914 --> 01:01:52,250
My daughter just did as her mother said.

950
01:01:58,339 --> 01:02:02,051
I can see why
