975
01:04:39,750 --> 01:04:41,669
I had to come as my girl got scared.

976
01:04:41,752 --> 01:04:44,297
Your boyfriend looks somewhat dangerous.

977
01:04:44,380 --> 01:04:45,548
I'm worried.

978
01:04:45,631 --> 01:04:47,800
So Professor Kang is your father?

979
01:04:47,884 --> 01:04:49,886
Attend my trial tomorrow.

